# Docker socket configuration for Testcontainers and docker-java.
#
# Uncomment and set the correct socket path for your Docker runtime:
#
# OrbStack (macOS):
#   -DDOCKER_HOST=unix:///Users/YOUR_USERNAME/.orbstack/run/docker.sock
#   -DTESTCONTAINERS_DOCKER_SOCKET_OVERRIDE=/Users/YOUR_USERNAME/.orbstack/run/docker.sock
#
# Docker Desktop (macOS / Windows):
#   -DDOCKER_HOST=unix:///var/run/docker.sock
#   -DTESTCONTAINERS_DOCKER_SOCKET_OVERRIDE=/var/run/docker.sock
#
# Linux (standard):
#   -DDOCKER_HOST=unix:///var/run/docker.sock
#
# On Linux CI (GitHub Actions, etc.) DOCKER_HOST is auto-detected by
# Testcontainers — no configuration needed here.
